Class JsonStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.baasbox.android.json.JsonStructure
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonArray, JsonObject

    public abstract class JsonStructure
extends java.lang.Object
    Represent JSON structured data, either a JsonObject or a JsonArray. Created by Andrea Tortorella on 01/01/14.
